{
  "analytics_identifier": null,
  "base_path": "/get-new-energy-certificate",
  "content_id": "e6134b0d-7835-449a-8a8b-3faf8fb5c858",
  "description": "Get a new energy certificate for your property: energy performance certificate (EPC), display energy certificate (DEC) or air conditioning inspection certificate. Find an assessor to get a certificate.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>To get a new energy certificate for your home, business property or a public building, you need to have it assessed.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>This service is also available <a href=\"/cael-tystysgrif-ynni-newydd\">in Welsh (Cymraeg)</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Arrange a property assessment to get a new:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>energy performance certificate (EPC)</li>\n  <li>display energy certificate (DEC) for a public building</li>\n  <li>air conditioning inspection certificate and report</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The cost of an assessment varies by assessor and the size of the property.</p>\n\n<p>After the assessment, the assessor will give you a digital copy of your certificate.</p>\n\n<p>You can also view or print an existing energy certificate.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"find-an-assessor\">Find an assessor</h2>\n\n<p>Find an accredited assessor for your home, business property or a public building. You can use this service in England, Wales or Northern Ireland.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There is a different process if you want to <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.scottishepcregister.org.uk/\">find an accredited assessor in Scotland.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>When you find an assessor:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>contact them directly to arrange a viewing</li>\n  <li>check that they’re part of an accredited scheme</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://getting-new-energy-certificate.service.gov.uk/find-an-assessor/type-of-property",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "what_you_need_to_know": "<p>You can <a href=\"/find-energy-certificate\">check if the property already has a valid energy certificate</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"get-help-finding-an-energy-assessor\">Get help finding an energy assessor</h3>\n\n<p>For help finding an assessor, contact the Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities (<abbr title=\"Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities\">DLUHC</abbr>).</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><a href=\"mailto:dluhc.digital-services@levellingup.gov.uk\">dluhc.digital-services@levellingup.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 020 3829 0748<br>\nMonday to Friday, 9am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-youre-unhappy-with-the-assessment\">If you’re unhappy with the assessment</h3>\n\n<p>You can complain to the assessor directly. If you’re still unhappy, you can contact the assessor’s accreditation scheme. Their contact details will be on the energy performance certificate.</p>\n\n",
    "will_continue_on": ""
  },
